The software BladeEnc has not an installer. It's a "zip file". Then, we create a 
directory, and we unzip "BladeEnc" inside.

File name: BEnc-0942-Win-i586.zip
Directory name: BladeEnc
Version: 0.94.2
Installed-Size: 239 Ko
Description: BladeEnc is a program to generate MP3 files from WAV, AIFF or RAW 
sound files. BladeEnc is available for most modern computer platforms, including
Windows, Linux, BeOS, MacOS, UnixWare, Solaris, FreeBSD, NetBSD, OpenBSD, OS/2 
and many more. 

Source: http://www2.arnes.si/~mmilut/BladeEnc.html

The file "installBladeEnc.bat" is useful of executable "shortcut.exe", to create
shortcuts.
Source: http://www.optimumx.com/download/#Shortcut